    SQLite++ is a C++ wrapper to SQLite library.

SQLite is a embedded database engine with very nice licence. It supports rich 
subset of SQL. For addition information on SQLite visit http://www.sqlite.org.

SQLite++ wraps only SQLite version 3.0 interface. For more information see 
documentation.

Library approaches with binding variables to SQL queries was inspired by 
Maciej Sobczak' SOCI wrapper (http://www.msobczak.com/prog/soci/).


Build and install instructions are placed in Install file.

Comments and suggestions are welcome.

    Pavel Medvedev <pm@despammed.com>